
@startuml
skinparam classAttributeIconColor Blue

class Player {
  -id: int
  -name: String
  -position: String (e.g., GK, LB)
  -attributes: Map<String, Integer>
}

class PlayerProfile {
  -id: int
  -targetPosition: String
  -requiredAttributes: Map<String, Integer>
}

class Scout {
  -id: int
  -name: String
  -role: String
}

class HeadScout {
  -id: int
  -name: String
}

class HeadCoach {
  -id: int
  -name: String
}

class Director {
  -id: int
  -name: String
}

class ScoutingAssignment {
  -id: int
  -player: Player
  -scout: Scout
  -dateAssigned: Date
  -status: String (e.g., pending, completed)
}

class ScoutingReport {
  -id: int
  -player: Player
  -scout: Scout
  -pros: String
  -cons: String
  -recommendation: String (e.g., key player, not a good signing)
  -dateSubmitted: Date
}

class LongList {
  -id: int
  -players: List<Player>
}

class ShortList {
  -id: int
  -players: List<Player>
}

class Offer {
  -id: int
  -player: Player
  -director: Director
  -status: String (e.g., made, accepted, rejected)
  -dateMade: Date
}

Player "1" --> "0..*" ScoutingAssignment : assigned to
Player "1" --> "0..*" ScoutingReport : reported by
PlayerProfile "1" --> "0..*" Player : matches profile
Scout "1" --> "0..*" ScoutingAssignment : performs
Scout "1" --> "0..*" ScoutingReport : submits
HeadScout "1" --> "1" ScoutingAssignment : assigns
HeadCoach "1" --> "0..*" PlayerProfile : creates
HeadCoach "1" --> "0..*" ShortList : manages
Director "1" --> "0..*" Offer : makes
LongList "1" --> "0..*" Player : contains
ShortList "1" --> "0..*" Player : contains
ScoutingAssignment "1" --> "1" ScoutingReport : results in
@enduml

---

### 📌 Explanation of Key Relationships:

- A **Player** can be assigned multiple **ScoutingAssignments**.
- A **Scout** can submit multiple **ScoutingReports**.
- A **PlayerProfile** may match multiple **Players**.
- A **HeadCoach** creates **PlayerProfiles** and manages the **ShortList**.
- A **HeadScout** assigns **ScoutingAssignments** and submits **ScoutingReports**.
- A **Director** makes **Offers** for players who are recommended for signing.
- A **LongList** contains multiple **Players**, which are later moved to the **ShortList** after evaluation.

